snippet.title: Revelations 1&2 Switch! - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Resident Evil Revelations 1&2 are now out for the Nintendo Switch! Will you be brave enough to venture through a wrecked ship or find a way to escape off Sushestvovanie Island?!
